metadata.name: Euro21NFT #England
metadata.description:
Euro21NFT was create to record this memorable Euro2020/2021 event. High collective value, limited supply to all the football & nft fans in the world. All unsold Euro21NFT will be burn after final match of Euro2020. Collector can redeem Unique ERC-721 and Mystical Euro21NFT on our website if they collect all 24 country Euro21NFT. 
Check us out at www.euro21nft.com
Find us in discord and twitter
